                <h3 class="subsection-title">Step 4: Wait for the REAL Fed Pivot Signal</h3>
                <p class="article-text">Don't buy the bro stock dip until you see <strong>ALL THREE signals:</strong>
                </p>
                <ol class="article-list">
                    <li><strong>Inflation sustainably below 2.5%</strong> for 3+ months</li>
                    <li><strong>Fed actually cuts rates</strong> (not just hints‚Äîactual cuts)</li>
                    <li><strong>Unemployment rising above 4.5%</strong> (recession fears = Fed panic = rate cuts)</li>
                </ol>
                <p class="article-text"><strong>Until then:</strong> Cash is king, value is safe, growth is death.</p>
